{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/signalgroup\/onnotifytarget(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyTarget"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject14SignalGroupRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/SignalGroupRef","text":"SignalGroupRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpecRef","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"notifyTarget","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}],"name":"handler"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C","type":"codeList